at the proposed concatenation provides a considerable performance\nboost relative to the existing error correcting system based on long\nBose-Chaudhuri-Hocquenghem (BCH) codes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Dec 2013 20:31:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-23"}
