mutativity could be presented at\nthe Compton wave length, in contrast to conventional expectations at the Planck\nlength. At last, we present the manifestly covariant form of spin and position\noperators of Dirac equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Dec 2013 12:37:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Jan 2014 14:59:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 Oct 2014 13:37:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-29"}
